'''Igures''' d yiwet n taddart i d yezgan di tɣiwant n [[At-Yeḥya]] di tanebdaḍt n Tala n Sila deg ugezdu n [[Tizi Wezzu]]

==Aẓar n w'awal==

==Amezruy==
[[Aɛmer Ubuyaḥya]] d yiwen umrabeḍ ,tezdeɣ tarwa-s tama n wasif ddaw Igures , di tgerwla mgal amnekcem afransis (1954) tefka d taddart 32 imeɣraṣen am [[Akli At Ṭayeb]] , [[Tasaɛdit At Ṭayeb]] , [[Muḥend Lɛerbi]] neɣ [[Busɛad Ujidan]]. Syina mi yefra ṭrad, ulin atas imezdaɣ d asawen seg wasif mi yuɣen tiferkiwin ɣer taddart n [[At Mlal]] id yezgan s ufella n Igures .

==Tarakalt==
Taddart Igures tesɛa tilisa nettat d [[At Mlal]], [[Ta_ɣiwant_n_At_Bu_Yusef|At Bu Yusef]] ([[Tifeṛḍud]])  [[Iferḥunen]](ibelqisen).


==Iderman==
Tebḍa taddart ɣef 4 n txelǧatin :
# At Ṭeyeb
# At Weftis
# Igujilen
# At Aɛmer

Degs 5 n yismawen n twacult:
# Ait Tayeb
# Oudjidane
# Ait Mouhoub
# Ait Moufek
# Ben Abderrahmane

==Tamudi==
Tesɛa taddart azal 850 imezdaɣ deg useggas 2013.




